title: Oceana
review:
Octopus is a little too dry. Dover sole is not good enough. They cut all the fins off which are tasty parts. I like the chicken and that it is ISDA certified organic. The beet salad is very good and tasty with yogurt and pistachio.

Good service. They fulfilled my request to use only olive oil for all my courses. By default they mix olive oil and canola oil to cook which is not up to par for me.
name: Hina Cao

title: Lure Fishbar
review:
We came for some oysters and wine, sadly the service this time was terrible!
We ordered a nice bottle of wine, it got poured once and the bottle was place on a wine cooler away from the table, the server never came around so we had to get up and serve the wine ourselves, not a great experience.
name: Nancy Cavazos
